source.name: EMS - Annual Incidents - 2012
source.description:
Annual EMS incidens for calendar 2012.  An incident is generated when a request for assistance is recieved, generally through 911.  An incident may generate multiple responses.

Note: Due to the methodological differences in data collection, different data sources may produce different results.
